Package com.ethanruffing.preferenceabstraction

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IPreferences
    An interface for a system for accessing a preferences store.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutoPreferences
    This class provides a layer of abstraction over the possible methods for storing preference data.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ConfigurationType
    An enumeration of possible configuration sources.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    PreferenceMigrationException
    This exception is thrown when errors occur during the process of converting from one type of preference storage to another.
    SettingNotFoundException
    This exception is thrown when an attempt is made to read a setting that cannot be found in the chosen preferences store.
